data.message: **Welcome to the GolmiEval Task!** Describe the highlighted piece on the board on the right so that another person could **uniquely** identify it.
If you're not sure which piece is the target, just click on it! If that's your target, I'll tell you so.
Once you're ready you can simply send your description with the chat on the bottom. You will see a total of 15 boards
Here's a little help: you can reference pieces according to this legend
N looks like a teal colored low-backed barstool
Y looks like a dark purple pistol pointing to the viewer's left
X looks like a grey plus sign
I is just a orange straight line
U is like a 'U' with shortened sides
Still 10 boards to go
P is a grey cigarette pack with two cigarettes sticking out of the top
That is your target
F is like a brown "L" with a piece jutting out of its back
U is a grey C
W looks like a piece of a brown staircase
N is that low backed bar stool again, but on it's back and now olive green
Still 5 boards to go. You almost made it!
Z looks like an olive green z
Y looks like a brown lower case L with a piece jutting out of the side.
this is a purple plus sign
That is your target
this is an olive green rectangle with a square chunk taken out of the lower left corner
this is a kelly green c
That was the last one, thank you very much for your help
The room is closing, thanky you for plaing
